rn IP developments have hamstrung the industry over</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745301-peptidream-opulent-dream-now-a-reality", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:26:03"}, {"id": "4745321", "title": "Where Do Stocks Go From Here?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multi exposure of abstract financial diagram on office buildings background, banking and accounting concept\" data-id=\"1316474343\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Igor Kutyaev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As Ferris Bueller famously said, \u201cLife moves pretty fast. If you don\u2019t stop and look around once in a while, you could miss it.\u201d</p> <p>In that spirit, we thought we\u2019d take a minute and look around at this</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745321-where-stocks-go-from-here", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:20:00"}]}